{"tid":2250953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爆買日延期 全民參與『拯救12港人』集會","createTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T03:02:44.000Z","uid":381081,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e50c3fe9b821816d25af5f60aa14d94818428f57","tid":2250953,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/027qzW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F027qzW1.jpg&h=786f90bd&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n【爆買日延期 全民參與『拯救12港人』集會 #SAVE12】<br />\n<br />\n感謝多位店主及同路人的鼓勵和期待，發起了活動數天，我們已收到數百黃店報名，反應相當熱烈。同時多位報名參與的黃店店主向我們反映，雖然有信心1026反應仍然熱烈，但由於與10.10全民感謝日相隔時間較短，憂慮沒有足夠空間讓消費者及店家「回氣」。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時我們也得悉12人關注組及家屬將於今個週末舉行網上集會，我們也期望香港人及支持者可以對12人被送中給予最大關注並參與其中。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們決定將活動順延一個月至11月26日（即美國感恩節），希望各位能支持這個決定。未來一個月，我們會繼續籌備相關工作及各項針對小店的宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n未填form嘅黃店盡快填喇～ 好快會有第二波嘅星級懲罰師撐場！<br />\n👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/join1026now\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fjoin1026now&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=5ce90283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/join1026now</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n#懲罰師 #1026爆買日 #黃色經濟圈 #支持小店 #SAVE12HKYOUTH<br />\nIG 📷 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/punish_xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpunish_xi&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=e140ec27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/punish_xi</a><br />\nTG 📨 <a href=\"https://t.me/punish_Xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpunish_Xi&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=7e4f8d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/punish_Xi</a>"},{"pid":"c4b05ecca1e6dec11b0d82de435fa3a9f15de696","tid":2250953,"uid":287051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi